#: ../../source/news/releases/0.x/announcing-0.8/index.rst:4
msgid ""
"This is a major release for Istio on the road to 1.0. There are a great "
"many new features and architectural improvements in addition to the usual"
" pile of bug fixes and performance improvements."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/news/releases/0.x/announcing-0.8/index.rst:8
